    "en": {
      "title": "The jeep that crashed into the gas station",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "According to Mirihana Police, an accident occurred when a luxury jeep rammed into the Madiwela petrol station, seriously injuring the pump operator and causing serious damage to a three-wheeler and two motorcycles, a pump at the petrol station and the petrol station.",
        "The injured pumper has been admitted to Kalubowila Teaching Hospital. The driver of the luxury jeep came from Pitakott and reached the Madiwela petrol station via Talavathugoda. Instead of braking, he stepped on the accelerator and rammed into the fuel station. He hit the fuel pump and hit the nearby pumper. The police say that there was.",
        "The driver of the luxury jeep has been arrested and will be produced before the court. On the instructions of Mr. Manjula Thushara, Chief Inspector of Police, Mirihana Headquarters, Chief Inspector of Police Chaminda Gajanayake, Station Commander of the Traffic Division, is conducting investigations."
      ],
